<item>
            <title>[LU-11180] sanity-lfsck test_29b failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11180</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Lai Siyao &amp;lt;lai.siyao@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/aa52d7cc-8fa8-11e8-8ee3-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/aa52d7cc-8fa8-11e8-8ee3-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;== sanity-lfsck test 29b: LFSCK can repair bad nlink count (2) ======================================= 22:03:53 (1532469833)&lt;br/&gt;
#####&lt;br/&gt;
The object&apos;s nlink attribute is smaller than the object&apos;s known&lt;br/&gt;
name entries count. The LFSCK will repair the object&apos;s nlink&lt;br/&gt;
attribute to match the known name entries count&lt;br/&gt;
#####&lt;br/&gt;
rm: cannot remove &apos;/mnt/lustre/.lustre/lost+found/MDT0000/&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200003ab2:0xa0:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;-P-0&apos;: Directory not empty&lt;br/&gt;
rm: cannot remove &apos;/mnt/lustre/.lustre/lost+found/MDT0001/&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x2400032e2:0xb:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;-P-0&apos;: Directory not empty&lt;br/&gt;
Inject failure stub on MDT0 to simulate the case that foo&apos;s&lt;br/&gt;
nlink attribute is smaller than its name entries count.&lt;br/&gt;
CMD: trevis-8vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param fail_loc=0x1626&lt;br/&gt;
fail_loc=0x1626&lt;br/&gt;
CMD: trevis-8vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param fail_loc=0&lt;br/&gt;
fail_loc=0&lt;br/&gt;
Trigger namespace LFSCK to repair the nlink count&lt;br/&gt;
CMD: trevis-8vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl lfsck_start -M lustre-MDT0000 -t namespace -r -A&lt;br/&gt;
Started LFSCK on the device lustre-MDT0000: scrub namespace&lt;br/&gt;
CMD: trevis-8vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl lfsck_query -t namespace -M lustre-MDT0000 -w |&lt;br/&gt;
		      awk &apos;/^namespace_mdts_completed/ &lt;/p&gt;
{ print \$2 }
&lt;p&gt;&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/aa84723c-8fa8-11e8-8ee3-52540065bddc/show_text&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/aa84723c-8fa8-11e8-8ee3-52540065bddc/show_text&lt;/a&gt; shows client2 hung and rebooted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
